text: Caumont-sur-Orne is a former commune. It is in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Le Hom.Arrêté préfectoral 22 December 2015 == References == ==Other websites== Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Caumont-sur-Orne
